Name: moderate short-term activity
Meaning: Expected level of activity for this IP address over the last 24 hours.

Name: moderate long-term activity
Meaning: Expected level of activity for this IP address over the past 90 days.

Name: moderate short-term activity on risky services
Meaning: Significant activity for this IP address to or from risky services over the last 24 hours (see risky services above for definition of that term).

Name: moderate long-term activity on risky services
Meaning: Significant activity on this IP address to or from risky services over the last 90 days (see risky services above for definition of that term).

Name: high short-term activity
Meaning: More than expected activity for this IP address over the last 24 hours.

Name: high long-term activity
Meaning: More than expected activity for this IP address over the past 90 days.

Name: high short-term activity on risky services
Meaning: Very significant activity for this IP address to or from risky services over the last 24 hours (see risky services above for definition of that term).

Name: high long-term activity on risky services
Meaning: Very significant activity on this IP address to or from risky services over the last 90 days (see risky services above for definition of that term).

Name: very high short-term activity
Meaning: Very frequent changes of IP address attributes in verification traffic on this number over the past 24 hours.

Name: very high long-term activity
Meaning: Very frequent changes of IP address attributes in verification traffic on this number over the past 90 days.

Name: short-term activity on risky services
Meaning: Changes of IP address attributes in verification traffic on risky services on this number over the past 24 hours.

Name: long-term activity on risky services
Meaning: Changes of IP address attributes in verification traffic on risky services on this number over the past 90 days.

Name: very high short-term activity on risky services
Meaning: Very frequent changes of IP address attributes in verification traffic on risky services on this number over the past 24 hours.

Name: very high long-term activity on risky services
Meaning: Very frequent changes of IP address attributes in verification traffic on risky services on this number over the past 90 days.
